## Thoughts

1. Deal with the balloons from the left to the right;
2. Be greedy in the way that, when we are shooting the left-most balloons, shoot as many balloons as possible;
3. That way, we need to sort the ballons according to their left position; then we accumulate as many balloons that overlap the same x-range as possible;
4. To accumulate balloons, we need to find their common x-range, which should be initialized with `[left[0], right[0]]` (the left and right of the current left-most balloon, inclusively), and then continue to narrow down the x-range with the next balloon until no balloon with common x-range is found.

--------------------

