Since we have to minimize the number of arrows. So we will try to shoot arrow in such manner that it will burst as many as balloon it can. So let's represent a point by (l,r). If we sort all points by r values and shoot the arrow on r value it will be always beneficial for us. Beacuse this shoot may burst the next few ballons and try to minimize the number of arrows.
