# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We can sort the array on the Xend coordinate and take the right most point that is the points[i][1] as arrow's Position and we skip all the intervals in which this current position lies and increment the count of arrow when arrow's position is less than points[i][0] i.e. Xstart. 
