sort and check intersection points.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. first of all sort the points matrix.
2. store all points in stack in form end of sorted ponts matrix.
3. make count, temp variable and make while loop and start poping pair store in staack. and update temp and increment count variables.
4. return count.


# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(nlogn)
