How to Solve this Que?
1) Sort the array on the basis of end points.
2) Initialize arrows = 1.
3) Take points[0][1] as your end.
4) Compare each starting point with end.
5) If startpoint > end then increment arrows and set end to the endpoint of that row.
6) Return arrows.

